Industry producers will be in attendance, so this will be a once in a lifetime opportunity to create connections for everyone in the Texas area!

 More surprises on the way! STAY TUNED!!

( Really me and @foreiignmoney  won lol) Shout out to everybody that's supporting me and I know it's many more great things to come with my beats and music!
